{"tid":1675925,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"模擬抗爭 VR 遊戲《光復香港》  最快在 11 月中上架 Steam","createTime":"2019-10-26T07:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T07:59:32.000Z","uid":223405,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1545f8dbda7535e3cbb085dc7bc237f1e1789b","tid":1675925,"uid":223405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"由香港人開發的模擬抗爭遊戲《光復香港》已完成開發，據稱會在 11 月中 在 遊戲平台 Steam 上架。VR 遊戲《光復香港》在 8 月底開始籌劃，近日已開發完成，正進行實測。今日（25日）就邀請了早前被暴雪禁制的電競選手 Blitzchung 聰哥 7 時開 Live 體驗遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n在遊戲內，玩家將成為一位抗爭者，以第一身視點走進抗爭最前線，感受前線面對危機四伏的環境，承面對警方追捕，受隨時被捕的風險。不過，遊戲開發團隊在早前接受《立場新聞》訪問時指，遊戲限制只守不攻，喚玩家「請不要抱著『遊戲』的期待。這不是娛樂性，也不是 cosplay。它形式雖然是『遊戲』，但其實是場景重現的沉浸式體驗（immersive experience）。」而且，因受制於 Steam 的發行條款，遊戲內容不得涉及罪行（例如襲警），開發團隊亦不希望營造虛假空間供人發洩，所以奉行「不被捕不流血」的原則，避免一切攻擊行為，以防守為主。<br />\n<br />\n玩家只能手持路牌製成的盾牌作防守，最多也是拾起催淚彈擲向遠方，並無攻擊能力。開發團隊在《立場新聞》訪問中承認，玩家並無明確任務和目標，若要作為「遊戲」的確比較「單調」，只能稱作生存遊戲，因要角色被捕或中彈才告完結，而「復活」過後，只是周而復始地「只守不攻」。不過，團隊代表形容這種「無指令又無助的危機感」正是前線抗爭者面對現實。<br />\n<br />\n開發團隊希望借此遊戲予人「體驗」成為前線，讓更多人了解示威者的心態，更期盼通過遊戲平台接觸海外「可能不關心香港，純粹喜歡打機」的玩家，將影響力推去更遠的地方。<br />\n<br />\n《光復香港》初步計劃不設手機版本；電腦版開放免費下載，鼓勵大眾體驗；VR 版本則定價約 100 港元。所有收入扣除成本之後，將全數捐予「星火同盟」，資助被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n開發團隊在本月中已將遊戲呈交 Steam 進行審核，預計需時 2 至 3 星期，最快 11 月可上架。團隊聲言若項目不獲上架，不排除直接釋出下載連結。<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n<br />\n直播 ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/25/vr-librate-hong-kong/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2Fvr-librate-hong-kong%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN5Fs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=6163c2f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/25/vr-librate-hong-kong/game-channel/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Liberate-Hong-Kong-Game-Team-109758453782933/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FLiberate-Hong-Kong-Game-Team-109758453782933%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN5Fs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=8bf94a1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/Liberate-Hong-Kong-Game-Team-109758453782933/</a>"},{"pid":"875053cd1a640fad3833bdf94f189591bf6aca5c","tid":1675925,"uid":223405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"新聞來源：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/25/vr-librate-hong-kong/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2Fvr-librate-hong-kong%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN5Fs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=6163c2f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/25/vr-librate-hong-kong/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"74cd61cc5f871ce41990c3703f44ac084eb6b9ad","tid":1675925,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"ba6e68c13911ba5a0672720931cc3f7f6f43c6a5","tid":1675925,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:37:42.000Z","msg":"有無VR設備推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97e14914c4c5ed0ffb05ab265e3bcac9a251d28","tid":1675925,"uid":121995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:41:23.000Z","msg":"好想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273f947af3fd56fadd6ba83cdb4439cbb724ba84","tid":1675925,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"我估玩完會心情更沉重，俾防暴爆頭，打爆眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8d292a97947c6166d6b85666813d5e5d0d352e","tid":1675925,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"vr版雖然唔貴<br />\n但係vr設備好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278c9bd1bf5bfcb8b39f23fae63f35f02c3eaa2c","tid":1675925,"uid":88578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":